{"tid":1266140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"七一係香港島既小心身子","createTime":"2019-06-29T13:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T13:05:26.000Z","uid":48673,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3a399a55adaece60d41d2a9e1e6fbcd308135767","tid":1266140,"uid":48673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:00:32.000Z","msg":"政府已經有好多相應防範7。1 <br />\n<br />\n1. 6月29 轉左中環海濱 做軍事用地 ， 入面放架坦克車都仲得🚛🚛<br />\n<br />\n2. 警方嚴陣怖防， 徽用演藝，會展，仲唔困哂你班友<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qgLuRPC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqgLuRPC.png&h=fe7ee43e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. G20 7。1之前已經完左，你地班友係咁落習大大面<br />\n會議一完 即刻調教下你班打爸仔， 落9我面丫嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以我地要改變一下個節奏，俾返一種好似有啲同之前啲對手唔同既感覺 <br />\n<br />\n好似打緊山王咁，有唔同既進擊手段<br />\n三分綫外有三井既三分波<br />\n籃底有櫻木搶籃<br />\n中間有流村既中間切入<br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不如轉場去旺角唱k</span><br />\n<br />\n而家有效既係所謂既「外國勢力」， show 俾其他人睇，而牽制中共，未必係正面衝擊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>要記得邊個係主要敵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而唔係不斷消磨香港內部人員</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Be water, my friend <br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力</span></span>"},{"pid":"9b1c0cefd8714fe9adac04a958df6c2f86814387","tid":1266140,"uid":55851,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:02:33.000Z","msg":"講埋啲廢話"},{"pid":"6f72d590b6b3bf3271af54b24d2eb38369583767","tid":1266140,"uid":47659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:05:26.000Z","msg":"海濱達地 如果鎮壓你地既話根本不提也罷<br />\n屌 解放軍總部根本睇晒69 612 616 621 食住花生準備777話求救就衝出黎碌你啦"}]}